{"tid":509204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國抵制聖誕】燒樹唔畀慶耶穌降生 逼學生Boxing day賀老毛誕辰","createTime":"2017-12-25T05:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T08:20:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"081e46322020b00ddc1d2a807e1a0a5aad9160f5","tid":509204,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/131314_3fcd67a1c46da6c99642183dfaf1bec2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F131314_3fcd67a1c46da6c99642183dfaf1bec2.jpeg&h=6e4a3b3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/131316_243af0a3177f5f4a56508f94d16c6a59.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F131316_243af0a3177f5f4a56508f94d16c6a59.jpeg&h=f434e6ec&s={SIZE}\" />十九大後內地再沒有聖誕節！當局直接出手打壓，發文件下令黨政共青組織、大學「抵制西方節日」，當局甚至動用專政力量強拆聖誕樹、燒聖誕樹等裝飾；又組織民眾上街遊行「反聖誕」。<br />\n<br />\n這股「抵制西方節日」更蔓延到小學，小學在課室發誓：「和洋節說『不』，拒絕洋節，從我做起，傳承文明，過中國節！」另一小學老師則在會議室問一眾學生，知否12月24日、25日和26日是甚麼節日？大部份學生回答：「平安夜」、「聖誕節」，但對於12月26日則答不上，只知道也與聖誕有關。老師訓斥學生，12月26日是中共前最高領導人毛澤東誕生日子，以後不准學生慶祝聖誕節，要慶祝的只有「毛爺爺的誕辰」。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古集寧一中教育處前日（22日）發出通知，指根據中共中央辦公廳、國務院辦公廳下發的《關於實施中華優秀傳統文化傳承發展工程的意見》，要求平安夜（24日）晚上自習，聖誕日（25日）周一全日自習，按課時安排正常進行教學活動。通告又寫明：「禁止一切與聖誕節有關的活動和行為！一經發現，沒收禮品，扣班級考核分3分，扣學生個人品行考核分10分！」周一下午德育課主題，則要求鑑賞毛澤東詩詞。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171224/57622574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F57622574&d=tChkqxY43xZa1fhjETCzml0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2ce2e354\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171224%2F57622574&h=929e0de1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171224/57622574</a>"},{"pid":"3056b8ad0564617f2a8a61da565c50f7c5dc36b3","tid":509204,"uid":11962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"越黎越痴線"},{"pid":"579d970bc29fc1262a4126798c3dee9ccc66cb9d","tid":509204,"uid":112583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:22:31.000Z","msg":"似啦似啦<br />\n<br />\n經濟又唔係好得<br />\n美國又大企業減稅，資金回流<br />\n<br />\n今次仲反埋西方文化"},{"pid":"85b72a3582a311a2931b71fae06aad8259e33d70","tid":509204,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"最驚唔知幾時燒到香港"},{"pid":"1f57a65c74b99dd679d2eaf0aa993103ad70c35d","tid":509204,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"雲海FB:<br />\n<br />\n中共今年禁止民眾過聖誕節，所謂不過洋節， 我腦裏面就閃起，咁你唔學日本人根據先秦做嘅春秋兩祭？ 咁你唔學南韓每年進行最完整嘅祭孔儀式？ 而你中國政府會學習 歐洲人嘅共產主義？！ 阿媽！我好亂呀！ 而尋晚我哋北京啲親戚，就係打電話嚟我屋企，祝我哋聖誕快樂！吹呀！"},{"pid":"8412d645097f853468702ebd2f467c168d2a9c60","tid":509204,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"呢個國家好似台小醜戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427afea88a4bf4e0f7352069ceba4ff796ba6f6c","tid":509204,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8412d645097f853468702ebd2f467c168d2a9c60","tid":509204,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"呢個國家好似台小醜戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"丑"},{"pid":"5ff21376728372a5cc71cb6b749c67d52c0cda62","tid":509204,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"咪慶祝西曆新年呀契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f0b0f01df52448ac625491d65c318ca5cf4da2","tid":509204,"uid":46061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:52:01.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n成班領導人影相換撚左啲西裝做唐裝先啦"